snippet.title: Footage of PokéPark: Fishing Contest DS (3)
snippet.description:
No I don't have a rom, I wish I did. I don't condone going out and harassing people who might own the rom, though I would love to see this publicly archived one day!

Originally recorded and published by user Buoysel of filb.de and PokéWiki.

It has been reuploaded on archive.org here: https://archive.org/details/tsuri-taikai

Also known unofficially as PokePark Fishing Rally DS

For more information and a lot of my own research, see https://chainswordcs.com
